reviewText: I ordered this DVD because it had Erin Avery.  Six women in eight scenes all solo.  Erin was in two as was Carli Banks.  A couple women aren't as open as the others but the show is a winner.
I really enjoyed this but just the price was alittle too high just for some unique show, I would buy it if it was less than 10 bucks other than that I had some fun with this
